ion, just under the 19.69 million Live+Same Day viewers on ABC and Hulu, pe=
r Nielsen. Pretty close! Alvaro is getting some status-defining Puck merch =
and the Wicked doll with the special error. Thanks to the hundreds of reade=
rs who submitted.

